      "blocks": [
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b0",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            503.3999938964844,
            70.5479736328125,
            543.3359375,
            87.73197174072266
          ],
          "text": "Annex",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "Arial-BoldMT",
            "flags": 16,
            "is_bold": true,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b1",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            71.99996948242188,
            98.2679443359375,
            543.3363647460938,
            129.31192016601562
          ],
          "text": "Master Direction on Penal Provisions in reporting of transactions/ balances at \nCurrency Chests",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "Arial-BoldMT",
            "flags": 16,
            "is_bold": true,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b2",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            71.99996948242188,
            139.96795654296875,
            207.9972381591797,
            157.15194702148438
          ],
          "text": "1. Reporting Procedure",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "Arial-BoldMT",
            "flags": 16,
            "is_bold": true,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b3",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            71.99996948242188,
            169.7879638671875,
            335.3761291503906,
            186.97195434570312
          ],
          "text": "1.1 Reporting of Currency Chest Transactions",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "Arial-BoldMT",
            "flags": 16,
            "is_bold": true,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b4",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            71.99996948242188,
            197.75999450683594,
            543.33984375,
            230.59201049804688
          ],
          "text": "The minimum amount of deposit into / withdrawal from currency chest will be ₹1,00,000 \nand thereafter, in multiples of ₹50,000.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b5",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            71.99996948242188,
            243.3480224609375,
            230.67721557617188,
            260.5320129394531
          ],
          "text": "1.2 Time limit for Reporting",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "Arial-BoldMT",
            "flags": 16,
            "is_bold": true,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b6",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            71.99993896484375,
            273.16802978515625,
            543.3359985351562,
            306.1920166015625
          ],
          "text": "1.2.1 The currency chests should invariably report all transactions through CyM – CC \nportal on the same day by 7 pm.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b7",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            71.99993896484375,
            318.9480285644531,
            335.3759460449219,
            336.13201904296875
          ],
          "text": "1.2.2 Relaxation on account of strike in banks",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "Arial-BoldMT",
            "flags": 16,
            "is_bold": true,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b15",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            245.36990356445312,
            335.3825378417969,
            365.90631103515625,
            455.9189147949219
          ],
          "text": "Withdrawn",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 28.0,
            "name": "Arial",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b8",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            71.99993896484375,
            348.96002197265625,
            543.338623046875,
            381.1800231933594
          ],
          "text": "Relaxation in the reporting period on account of strike situation will be considered on \ncase-to-case basis.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b9",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            71.99990844726562,
            394.488037109375,
            543.3372192382812,
            425.5320129394531
          ],
          "text": "2. Delayed Reporting / Wrong Reporting / Non-Reporting of Currency Chest \nTransactions",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "Arial-BoldMT",
            "flags": 16,
            "is_bold": true,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b10",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            71.99990844726562,
            436.1880187988281,
            222.03713989257812,
            453.37200927734375
          ],
          "text": "2.1 Levy of penal interest",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "Arial-BoldMT",
            "flags": 16,
            "is_bold": true,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b11",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            71.99990844726562,
            463.968017578125,
            214.71591186523438,
            481.1520080566406
          ],
          "text": "2.1.1 Delay in Reporting",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "Arial-BoldMT",
            "flags": 16,
            "is_bold": true,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b12",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            71.9998779296875,
            491.82000732421875,
            543.3446044921875,
            563.4600219726562
          ],
          "text": "In the event of delay in reporting currency chest transactions, penal interest at the rate \nindicated in paragraph 4 of this circular shall be levied on the amount due from the chest \nholding bank for the period of delay. Penal interest shall be calculated on T+0 basis i.e. \npenal interest shall be levied in respect of transactions not reported by currency chests \nto the Issue Office on the same business day within the time limit prescribed above.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b13",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            71.99990844726562,
            574.72802734375,
            199.2959747314453,
            591.9120483398438
          ],
          "text": "2.1.2 Wrong reporting",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "Arial-BoldMT",
            "flags": 16,
            "is_bold": true,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b14",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            71.99990844726562,
            602.6400146484375,
            543.34228515625,
            715.6800537109375
          ],
          "text": "Penal interest shall be levied in respect of cases of wrong reporting in the same manner \ntill the date of receipt of corrected advice by Reserve Bank. As debits/credits to banks' \ncurrent accounts are raised on the basis of the transactions reported by the currency \nchests, penal interest shall invariably be levied in all cases of wrong reporting by the \ncurrency chests. It is expected that currency chests would ensure the correctness of \nfigures reported on the CyM - CC portal. Particular care shall be taken to ensure that \nremittances of fresh notes/re-issuable notes sent to the currency chests from RBI/press \nare not reported as 'deposit' transactions.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        }
      ],
      "links": []
    },
    {
      "page_number": 3,
      "width": 612.0,
      "height": 792.0,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "block_id": "p3_b0",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            72.0,
            70.5479736328125,
            460.115966796875,
            87.73197174072266
          ],
          "text": "2.1.3 Inclusion of ineligible amounts in the currency chest balances",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "Arial-BoldMT",
            "flags": 16,
            "is_bold": true,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p3_b1",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            72.0,
            98.39994812011719,
            543.34228515625,
            142.43991088867188
          ],
          "text": "(i) Penal interest shall be levied in all cases where the bank has enjoyed 'ineligible' credit \nin its current account with Reserve Bank on account of wrong reporting / delayed reporting \n/ non-reporting of transactions.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p3_b2",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            72.0,
            153.83995056152344,
            543.3423461914062,
            253.01986694335938
          ],
          "text": "(ii) Only cash held in the custody of joint custodians and 'freely available' to them is eligible \nfor inclusion in the chest balances. Thus, cash kept for safe custody in sealed covers for \nwhatever reasons/cash in trunks/bins under the lock and key of any official/s other than \nthe Joint Custodians or bearing a third lock put by any official in addition to the two locks \nof the Joint Custodians is not eligible for being included in the chest balances. If such \namounts are included in the chest balances, these shall be treated as instances of wrong \nreporting and shall attract penal interest at the rate specified in paragraph 4.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p3_b3",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            72.0,
            264.4198913574219,
            543.341064453125,
            322.2598571777344
          ],
          "text": "(iii) In all the above cases (excepting shortages in chest balances / remittances, shortages \ndue to pilferage / frauds, counterfeit banknotes detected in chest balances / remittances), \npenal interest shall be levied from the date of inclusion of 'ineligible' amounts in chest \nbalances till the exclusion of such amounts from chest balances.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p3_b4",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            72.0,
            333.5278625488281,
            321.39739990234375,
            350.71185302734375
          ],
          "text": "2.1.4 Penal measures for other deficiencies",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "Arial-BoldMT",
            "flags": 16,
            "is_bold": true,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p3_b13",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            245.36990356445312,
            335.3825378417969,
            365.90631103515625,
            455.9189147949219
          ],
          "text": "Withdrawn",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 28.0,
            "name": "Arial",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p3_b5",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            72.0,
            361.3798522949219,
            543.3399047851562,
            405.4198303222656
          ],
          "text": "Penal measures for shortages in chest balances / remittances, shortages due to pilferage \n/ frauds, counterfeit banknotes detected in chest balances / remittances shall be taken on \nthe basis of prevailing “Scheme of Penalties”.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p3_b6",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            72.0,
            416.7478332519531,
            176.01600646972656,
            433.93182373046875
          ],
          "text": "3. Levy of penalty",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "Arial-BoldMT",
            "flags": 16,
            "is_bold": true,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p3_b7",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            72.0,
            444.52783203125,
            342.6960144042969,
            461.7118225097656
          ],
          "text": "3.1 Reporting of soiled note remittances to RBI",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "Arial-BoldMT",
            "flags": 16,
            "is_bold": true,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p3_b8",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            72.0,
            472.37982177734375,
            543.3387451171875,
            516.4197998046875
          ],
          "text": "Soiled note remittances to RBI shall not be shown as withdrawal by chest(s). In case such \nremittances to RBI are wrongly reported as 'withdrawal', a penalty of ₹50,000 shall be \nlevied irrespective of the value of remittance and period of such wrong reporting.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p3_b9",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            72.0,
            527.747802734375,
            340.0559997558594,
            544.9318237304688
          ],
          "text": "3.2 Reporting of diversions in CyM – CC portal",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "Arial-BoldMT",
            "flags": 16,
            "is_bold": true,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p3_b10",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            72.0,
            555.599853515625,
            543.34228515625,
            627.2398681640625
          ],
          "text": "All currency chest diversions (both between chests of the same bank and between chests \nof different banks) have to be reported through ‘Diversion Module’ of CyM-CC Portal. The \nCC sending the diversion should initiate the diversion entry. The receiving CC should \nacknowledge the same. Diversions should not be reported as deposit/withdrawal. A \npenalty of ₹50,000 shall be levied for any such wrong reporting.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p3_b11",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            72.0,
            638.5078125,
            437.43597412109375,
            655.6918334960938
          ],
          "text": "3.3 Delayed reporting where currency chests had “Net Deposit”",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "Arial-BoldMT",
            "flags": 16,
            "is_bold": true,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p3_b12",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            72.0,
            666.35986328125,
            543.34228515625,
            710.33984375
          ],
          "text": "Penal interest at the prevailing rate for delayed reporting of the instances where the \ncurrency chest had reported “net deposit” shall not be charged. However, in order to \nensure proper discipline in reporting currency chest transactions, a flat penalty of ₹50,000",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        }
      ],
      "links": []
    },
    {
      "page_number": 4,
      "width": 612.0,
      "height": 792.0,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "block_id": "p4_b0",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            72.0,
            70.61997985839844,
            543.3385620117188,
            100.8599624633789
          ],
          "text": "shall be levied on the currency chests for delayed reporting, irrespective of the value of \nnet deposit.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p4_b1",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            72.00000762939453,
            112.12799072265625,
            210.69601440429688,
            129.31198120117188
          ],
          "text": "4. Rate of penal interest",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "Arial-BoldMT",
            "flags": 16,
            "is_bold": true,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p4_b2",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            71.99996948242188,
            140.0399627685547,
            543.3400268554688,
            184.07992553710938
          ],
          "text": "Penal interest shall be levied at the rate of 2% over the prevailing Bank Rate for the period \nof delayed reporting/wrong reporting/non-reporting /inclusion of ineligible amounts in \nchest balances.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p4_b3",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            71.99996948242188,
            195.2879638671875,
            416.1399230957031,
            212.47195434570312
          ],
          "text": "5. Operational Guidelines on levy of penalties/penal interest",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "Arial-BoldMT",
            "flags": 16,
            "is_bold": true,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p4_b4",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            71.99996948242188,
            221.98797607421875,
            214.59716796875,
            239.17196655273438
          ],
          "text": "5.1 Competent Authority",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "Arial-BoldMT",
            "flags": 16,
            "is_bold": true,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p4_b5",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            71.99996948242188,
            256.66796875,
            543.3399658203125,
            300.8399353027344
          ],
          "text": "The Competent Authority to decide the nature of irregularity shall be the Officer-in-\nCharge of the Issue Department of the Regional Office under whose jurisdiction the \ndefaulting currency chest is located.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p4_b6",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            72.0,
            312.0479431152344,
            206.01600646972656,
            329.23193359375
          ],
          "text": "5.2 Appellate Authority",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "Arial-BoldMT",
            "flags": 16,
            "is_bold": true,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p4_b11",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            245.36990356445312,
            335.3825378417969,
            365.90631103515625,
            455.9189147949219
          ],
          "text": "Withdrawn",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 28.0,
            "name": "Arial",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p4_b7",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            71.99996948242188,
            346.7279357910156,
            543.3411865234375,
            446.15985107421875
          ],
          "text": "5.2.1 As the sole criterion for levy of penal interest/ penalty for delayed reporting is the \nnumber of days of delay, there should ordinarily be no occasion for banks to request for \nreconsideration of the Reserve Bank's decision. However, representations, if any, on \naccount of genuine difficulties faced by currency chests especially in hilly/remote areas \nand those affected by natural calamities, etc., may be made to the Regional Director/Chief \nGeneral Manager/Officer-in-Charge of the Regional Office concerned through the Head / \nControlling office of the bank within a month from the date of debit.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p4_b8",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            72.0,
            457.307861328125,
            543.3386840820312,
            487.7398376464844
          ],
          "text": "5.2.2 In the case of wrong reporting representations for waiver shall not be considered. \n{cf. para 2.1.2 above}.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p4_b9",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            72.0,
            498.8878479003906,
            543.3399047851562,
            598.3198852539062
          ],
          "text": "5.2.3 As the intention behind the levy of penal interest/ penalty is to inculcate discipline \namong banks so as to ensure prompt/correct reporting, requests by banks for waiver of \npenal interest on grounds that delayed/wrong/non-reporting did not result in utilization of \nthe Reserve Bank's funds or shortfall in the maintenance of CRR/SLR or that they were \nthe result of clerical mistakes, unintentional or arithmetical errors, first time error, \ninexperience of staff etc., shall not be considered as valid grounds for waiver of penal \ninterest.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p4_b10",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            216.0,
            609.7198486328125,
            319.2359924316406,
            626.099853515625
          ],
          "text": "-------------------------",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        }
      ],
